{
  "stem": "26022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Of course, you know, in those days, we didn't have the star yet-- no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm on the sidewalk with a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A big sewing machine, built-in, you know, with-- with-- in a chest and with-- with the shelves so we could-- you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a big piece of furniture, relatively speaking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] How do I get it from here to there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It so happened that-- as I said, we had so many good friends of various denominations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a friend who-- always thought she was Aryan, was brought up Catholic, was in love with a man who joined the party, thought she could marry him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she was a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when she wanted to marry him, it turned out that her grandparents had been baptized, but actually, they were Jews, which she never knew, and which she apologized.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she really didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Albright-- ?] you know, I mean, this is not unusual.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so she was considered a half-Aryan, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She could keep her firm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She could keep everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She raised her-- everything was fine, except she couldn't marry a Nazi functionary, and she couldn't do several things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But she had two strong brothers with the same background who served in the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, they had all the obligations of full Aryans, but none of the-- not all of the privileges.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I knew that her name was also Liesl, of course, so I knew that she had these strong brothers, and they could possibly do something with this heavy sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I called from the street, telephone, with the sewing machine standing on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If somebody would want to take it, take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I wouldn't make any fuss over it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
